Raylib stays
ImGui stays

Src structure
    src/lib
        pack: multiple animations

    src/editor
        editor: interaction with main picture, needs pack
        modes: different editing modes
    
    src/ui
        ui: imgui elements
        windows: namespace Sk::!
            imgui windows, needs lib/..

    src/util -> Global static helpers for Raylib

    src/imgui -> Global static helpers for ImGui
